permanent <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">secretary</ENAMEX> of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Academie Royale des Sciences des Lettres et des</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Beaux-arts de Belgique</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Brussels</ENAMEX>, to <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Guido Crapanzano</ENAMEX>, rector of the
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Instituto di Scienze della Comunicazione</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Milan</ENAMEX>. <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Last July</TIMEX> the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">jury</ENAMEX> picked a
