            The winning <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">designer</ENAMEX> went
for the "ages and styles" theme, interpreted as such stock architectural
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">elements</ENAMEX> as <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">bridges</ENAMEX>, windows, and gateways. The <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">eight ages</TIMEX> in which these
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">bridges</ENAMEX>, windows, and gateways appear are <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Classical</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Romanesque</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Gothic</ENAMEX>,
